#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rename.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rename"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:1 of
msgid "Alter axes labels."
msgstr "更改轴标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:3 of
msgid ""
"Function / dict values must be unique (1-to-1). Labels not contained in a"
" dict / Series will be left as-is. Extra labels listed don't throw an "
"error."
msgstr ""
"函数/字典的值必须是唯一的（一对一）。不在字典/Series中的标签将保持原样。"
"列出的额外标签不会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:7 of
msgid ""
"Dict-like or functions transformations to apply to that axis' values. Use"
" either ``mapper`` and ``axis`` to specify the axis to target with "
"``mapper``, or ``index`` and ``columns``."
msgstr ""
"应用于该轴值的类字典或函数变换。使用 ``mapper`` 和 ``axis`` 指定目标轴，"
"或使用 ``index`` 和 ``columns``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:12 of
msgid ""
"Alternative to specifying axis (``mapper, axis=0`` is equivalent to "
"``index=mapper``)."
msgstr "指定轴的替代方式（``mapper, axis=0`` 等同于 ``index=mapper``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:15 of
msgid ""
"Alternative to specifying axis (``mapper, axis=1`` is equivalent to "
"``columns=mapper``)."
msgstr "指定轴的替代方式（``mapper, axis=1`` 等同于 ``columns=mapper``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:18 of
msgid ""
"Axis to target with ``mapper``. Can be either the axis name ('index', "
"'columns') or number (0, 1). The default is 'index'."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``mapper`` 指定的目标轴。可以是轴名称（'index', 'columns'）或数字（0"
", 1）。默认为 'index'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:21 of
msgid "Also copy underlying data."
msgstr "同时复制底层数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:23 of
msgid "Whether to return a new DataFrame. If True then value of copy is ignored."
msgstr "是否返回一个新的 DataFrame。如果为 True，则忽略 copy 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:26 of
msgid "In case of a MultiIndex, only rename labels in the specified level."
msgstr "对于 MultiIndex，仅重命名指定层级中的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:29 of
msgid ""
"If 'raise', raise a `KeyError` when a dict-like `mapper`, `index`, or "
"`columns` contains labels that are not present in the Index being "
"transformed. If 'ignore', existing keys will be renamed and extra keys "
"will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"如果为 'raise'，当类字典的 `mapper`、`index` 或 `columns` 包含不在被转换"
"索引中的标签时，将引发 `KeyError`。如果为 'ignore'，现有键将被重命名，"
"多余键将被忽略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:36 of
msgid "DataFrame with the renamed axis labels."
msgstr "具有重命名轴标签的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:39 of
msgid ""
"If any of the labels is not found in the selected axis and     "
"\"errors='raise'\"."
msgstr "如果在所选轴中找不到任何标签且 \"errors='raise'\"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.rename_axis`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:44 of
msgid "Set the name of the axis."
msgstr "设置轴的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:47 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:48 of
msgid "``DataFrame.rename`` supports two calling conventions"
msgstr "``DataFrame.rename`` 支持两种调用约定"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:50 of
msgid "``(index=index_mapper, columns=columns_mapper, ...)``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:51 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``(mapper, axis={'index', 'columns'}, ...)``"
msgstr "``(mapper, axis={'index', 'columns'}, ...)`"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:53 of
msgid "We *highly* recommend using keyword arguments to clarify your intent."
msgstr "我们 *强烈* 推荐使用关键字参数以明确意图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:56 of
msgid "Rename columns using a mapping:"
msgstr "使用映射重命名列："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:66 of
msgid "Rename index using a mapping:"
msgstr "使用映射重命名索引："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:74 of
msgid "Cast index labels to a different type:"
msgstr "将索引标签转换为不同类型："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.rename.df_rename:85 of
msgid "Using axis-style parameters"
msgstr "使用轴样式的参数"

